#View(data)
mexico <- filter(data, country == "Mexico")
mexico <- filter(mexico, year > 1989)
mexico <- filter(mexico, year < 2014)
mexico <- mexico[,c(-1,-4,-7,-8,-9,-12,-13,-14,-15,-16,-18,-23,-24, -25, -26, -27, -28)]
names(mexico) <- c("year", "sex", "suicides_no", "population", "gdp_for_year", "gdp_per_capita", "life_expectancy_years", "public_health_exp_GDP","share_whith_alcohol_disorders",  "share_whith_anxiety_disorders", "share_with_mental_disorders")
mexico$life_expectancy_years <- as.double(mexico$life_expectancy_years)
mexico$public_health_exp_GDP <- as.double(mexico$public_health_exp_GDP)
mexico$share_whith_alcohol_disorders <- as.double(mexico$share_whith_alcohol_disorders)
mexico$share_whith_anxiety_disorders <- as.double(mexico$share_whith_anxiety_disorders)
mexico$share_with_mental_disorders <- as.numeric(unlist(mexico$share_with_mental_disorders))
mexico <- mexico %>% group_by(year, sex) %>% summarise(suicides_no = sum(suicides_no), population = sum(population), gdp_for_year = mean(gdp_for_year), gdp_per_capita = mean(gdp_per_capita), life_expectancy_years = mean(life_expectancy_years),public_health_exp_GDP = mean(public_health_exp_GDP), share_whith_alcohol_disorders = mean(share_whith_alcohol_disorders), share_whith_anxiety_disorders = mean(share_whith_anxiety_disorders), share_with_mental_disorders = mean(share_with_mental_disorders) )

Suicidios

# Crear tibble para la grfica lineal 
overall_tibble <- mexico %>%
  select(year, suicides_no, population) %>%
  group_by(year) %>%
  summarise(suicide_capita = round((sum(suicides_no)/sum(population))*100000, 2)) 


# Crear grfica en modo serie de tiempo
highchart() %>% 
    hc_add_series(overall_tibble, hcaes(x = year, y = suicide_capita, color = suicide_capita), type = "line") %>%
    hc_tooltip(crosshairs = TRUE, borderWidth = 1.5, headerFormat = "", pointFormat = paste("Ao: <b>{point.x}</b> <br> Suicidio: <b>{point.y}</b>")) %>%
    hc_title(text = "Suicidios en Mxico por ao") %>% 
    hc_subtitle(text = "1990-2013") %>%
    hc_xAxis(title = list(text = "Ao")) %>%
    hc_yAxis(title = list(text = "Suicidios por cada 100k personas"),
             allowDecimals = FALSE,
             plotLines = list(list(
                    color = "black", width = 1, dashStyle = "Dash", 
                    value = mean(overall_tibble$suicide_capita),
                    label = list(text = "Promedio = 4.015", 
                                 style = list(color = "black", fontSize = 11))))) %>%
    hc_legend(enabled = FALSE) %>% 
    hc_add_theme(custom_theme)

Suicidios por por gnero

# Crer tible para sex
sex_tibble <- mexico %>%
  select(year, sex, suicides_no, population) %>%
  group_by(year, sex) %>%
  summarise(suicide_capita = round((sum(suicides_no)/sum(population))*100000, 2))

# Color
sex_color <- c("#43FF33","#33C3FF" ) 

# Grfica
highchart() %>% 
    hc_add_series(sex_tibble, hcaes(x = year, y = suicide_capita, group = sex), type = "line", color = sex_color) %>%
    hc_tooltip(crosshairs = TRUE, borderWidth = 1.5, headerFormat = "", pointFormat = paste("Year: <b>{point.x}</b> <br>","Gender: <b>{point.sex}</b><br>", "Suicides: <b>{point.y}</b>")) %>%
    hc_title(text = "Suicidios por gnero") %>% 
    hc_subtitle(text = "1985-2016") %>%
    hc_xAxis(title = list(text = "Ao")) %>%
    hc_yAxis(title = list(text = "Suicidios por cada 100K personas"),
             allowDecimals = FALSE,
             plotLines = list(list(
                    color = "black", width = 1, dashStyle = "Dash",
                    value = 4.015,
                    label = list(text = "Promedio = 4.015", 
                                 style = list(color = 'black', fontSize = 11))))) %>% 
    hc_add_theme(custom_theme)

names(mexico)

mexico_tidy <- pivot_wider(mexico, names_from = sex, 
  values_from = population)
mexico_tidy$female <- replace_na(mexico_tidy$female,0)
mexico_tidy$male <- replace_na(mexico_tidy$male,0)
mexico_tidy <- mexico_tidy %>% group_by(year) %>% summarise(suicides_no = sum(suicides_no), gdp_for_year = mean(gdp_for_year), gdp_per_capita = mean(gdp_per_capita), life_expectancy_years = mean(life_expectancy_years),public_health_exp_GDP = mean(public_health_exp_GDP), share_whith_alcohol_disorders = mean(share_whith_alcohol_disorders), share_whith_anxiety_disorders = mean(share_whith_anxiety_disorders), share_with_mental_disorders = mean(share_with_mental_disorders), female = sum(female), male = sum(male) )
ggplot(mexico_tidy) + aes(year, life_expectancy_years) + geom_line(color = "red") + geom_point()+ labs(title = "Esperanza de vida", x = "aos", y = "")

ggplot(mexico_tidy) + aes(year, share_whith_alcohol_disorders) + geom_line(color = "purple") + geom_point()+ labs(title = "Porcentaje de la poblacin con alcoholismo", x = "aos", y = "% Poblacin")

ggplot(mexico_tidy) + aes(year, share_whith_anxiety_disorders) + geom_line(color = "green") + geom_point()+ labs(title = "Porcentaje de la poblacin con transtornos de ansiedad", x = "aos", y = "% Poblacin")

ggplot(mexico_tidy) + aes(year, share_with_mental_disorders) + geom_line(color = "pink") + geom_point()+ labs(title = "Porcentaje de la poblacin con transtornos mentales", x = "aos", y = "% Poblacin")
